dct_title_s: Andorra mapa topogràfic 1:25 000: / Govern d'Andorra, Ministeri d'economia i territori, Àrea de cartografia.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours, and spot heights. Map shows road, transportation and cultural features, points of interest, forests, legend. Ancillary maps: map of administrative boundaries and location map. Map shows administrative boundaries, tourist sites, and leisure information.
dct_creator_sm: Andorra. Ministeri d'ordenament territorial. Àrea de cartografia i topografia
dct_publisher_sm: Andorra la Vella : Cartografia Oficial d'Andorra, 2014.
